<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV40">
<l>āṉaikātto rāṉaikoṉṟa taṉṟiyāyar piḷḷaiyā</l>
<l>yāṉaimēytti yāṉeyuṇṭi yaṉṟukuṉṟa moṉṟiṉāl</l>
<l>āṉaikāttu maiyarikkaṇ mātarārti ṟattumuṉ</l>
<l>āṉaiyaṉṟu ceṉṟaṭartta māyameṉṉa māyamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You protected an elephant. Other than that, becoming a cowherd boy,</l>
<l>[You] killed an elephant; You grazed cattle, and ate cow’s ghee.</l>
<l>And that day, You protected the cattle with a hill.</l>
<l>And going on that day before the lady with kohled eyes with [red] streaks,</l>
<l rend="indent">You destroyed the bulls. What wonder is that?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
